graph TB
    subgraph Client Workstation
        Browser[Web Browser<br/>Chrome / Edge / Firefox]
    end

    subgraph Docker Host / Cloud Server
        subgraph Frontend Container
            NextApp[Next.js + TypeScript<br/>Bun Runtime<br/>Port 3000]
        end

        subgraph Backend Container
            FastAPI[FastAPI Application<br/>Python 3.11+<br/>Uvicorn ASGI Server]
            DocProc[Document Processor<br/>Docling]
            JWTAuth[JWT Authentication<br/>3-Tier RBAC<br/>bcrypt + HS256]
        end

        subgraph Database Container
            PG[(PostgreSQL 16<br/>pgvector + ParadeDB<br/>Hybrid Search<br/>Metadata + Query Logs)]
        end
    end

    subgraph External API Services
        EmbedAPI[Embedding Service<br/>Qwen3-Embedding-0.6B<br/>Google Colab + ngrok]
        CohereRerank[Cohere Rerank v3.5<br/>Result Reranking]
    end

    Browser -->|HTTP| NextApp
    NextApp -->|HTTP / REST API| FastAPI
    FastAPI -->|SQL / pgvector / ParadeDB| PG
    FastAPI -->|HTTPS| CohereRerank
    FastAPI -->|HTTP| EmbedAPI
    FastAPI --> DocProc
    FastAPI --> JWTAuth
